<div style="text-align: left; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 48px;">
  <div style="width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <h1>Enrollment Checkbox</h1>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
      This plugin places a checkbox on the student confirmation page when certain conditions are met.
      The student must check the checkbox in order to continue.
      In this example, the checkbox is shown to students who are younger than 15 1/2 on the course date.
    </p>
    <img src="/administrator/images/enroll_checkbox.png" alt="Enroll Checkbox" style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #D8D8D8; max-width: 618px;">
    <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
      The plugin can also block the student from enrolling under certain conditions.
      In this example, if the student selects "Obtain Driving Permit" as their reason for enrollment they will be blocked even if they check the box.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>